1.0.name: wordpress/agentpress-broker-listings
1.0.description:
1. The AgentPress Broker Listings plugin adds broker details as a metabox in your AgentPress Listings, shortcodes to list broker details and widgets to display a broker details.

  2. Using widget you can display broker details property-wise.

  3. Shortcode [agents] used to list of all brokers.

  4. Can able to filter list of properties agent-wise.

Note:

It requires AgentPress Listings Plugin to work.

Support

agastya.izone@gmail.com

If you like the plugin then don't forget to rate.
